REM FINGER-M.SCR v1.10 "Finger by mail"
rem By Steve Harris (steveha@cix), amended by pw@cix 28/10/97
status "Sending Finger Request..."
put "mail"
waitfor "l:"
put "to getweb@info.lanic.utexas.edu"
waitfor "Enter subject:"
put "Finger request"
waitfor ".<CR>"
putnocr "GET http://www.mit.edu:8001/finger?"
put "%s('Finger By Mail','Specify address to finger:')"
put "."
waitfor "send/action:"
putnocr "cc "
put name
waitfor "send/action:"
put "send"
waitfor "l:"
put "q"
status ""
end